wide array of public services, including a separate banking sector that ope=
rated outside the international banking system.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:24px;color:#2A3034;margin:1em 0">Hezbollah=E2=80=99=
s reputation was derived primarily from its armed wing, which was seen as a=
n efficient military machine that compared favorably with the militaries of=
 midsized countries. However, after its defeat in the war with Israel in 20=
