ncourage Lebanese officials to honor their commitment to disarm Hezbollah. =
He warned them that Israel had a green light from U.S. President Donald Tru=
mp to attack Lebanon again if Hezbollah did not abide by its commitments. F=
ollowing his visit, U.S. envoy Tom Barrack arrived in Beirut. He emphasized=
 that Hezbollah's disarmament is an internal Lebanese issue, hinting that t=
he U.S. would not engage in dialogue with Hezbollah on the matter and that =
